Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:43.89,Title2,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\pos(650,120)\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HA86127&}Магический {\c&HC29E45&}Индекс
